I have a new install that I am unable to build code on. The closest I’ve been able to find to a similar problem is here, but it doesn’t seem to be the exact same problem: Gradle failing to build

I removed all previously installed associated software before installing.

All software is a fresh install with the most recent versions available.

I create a new project using the Timed Robot template. I’ve made no changes to the code.

I’ve been pulling my hair out for 2 days trying to figure this out and I’m making zero progress.
